setDetails.setDescription: Hate sitting through 30-50% drawdown when the market turns bearish? ECO hates that too. ECO is a TA based, discretionary ethereum eco system swing trading strategy that plans to capture as much macro-trend upside as possible whilst executing a rebalance into USDC when the market starts to lose momentum to limit drawdown.
setDetails.managerDescription: Crypto Kai is a crypto based content creator, community and core Set advocate. Come join us on YouTube and Discord where we document our Set investing journey!
